To obtain stoichiometric MBI, we have to consider the different volumetric molecular densities (mol/cm³) of MAI (CH3NH3I) and BiI3. With respect to the molar weights M and densities d of both precursors (MMAI = 159 g/mol, dMAI≈\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
